>> Come with me.

00:55:16.340 --> 00:55:17.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Let's have a look.

00:55:17.280 --> 00:55:18.322 align:middle line:90%
So what have we got?

00:55:18.322 --> 00:55:19.280 align:middle line:90%
>> So what have we got?

