00:55:52.754 --> 00:55:57.230 align:middle line:84%
>> It catapulted you out of
this lower percentile here,

00:55:57.230 --> 00:55:58.470 align:middle line:90%
all the way over to here--

00:55:58.470 --> 00:55:59.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:55:59.270 --> 00:56:00.690 align:middle line:90%
>> --within the normal range.

00:56:00.690 --> 00:56:02.510 align:middle line:84%
And in fact, you're
sitting in between two

00:56:02.510 --> 00:56:05.390 align:middle line:84%
