with their microbiomes.

00:56:05.390 --> 00:56:08.540 align:middle line:84%
So you've really increased
your biodiversity

00:56:08.540 --> 00:56:11.450 align:middle line:84%
in a very healthful
way during that time.

00:56:11.450 --> 00:56:14.720 align:middle line:84%
>> From what you found
of their microbiomes,

00:56:14.720 --> 00:56:19.580 align:middle line:84%
what could you sort of
ascertain that they eat?

00:56:19.580 --> 00:56:21.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, their diet
looks to be very,

00:56:21.930 --> 00:56:25.125 align:middle line:84%
very different to what
